<emphasis id="A8ECEAA1FFFAFFA3FABFF410FA7A3BE2" bold="true" box="[1390,1500,3010,3043]" pageId="4" pageNumber="497">Habitat.</emphasis>
Puna-like Andean vegetation of short-grass and shrubs at elevations of¢.3000 m.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
